			<div class="content" id="post-content-4331819">
									

<p>Wahoo!</p>
<p>It's been a rollercoaster ride putting this whole thing together. Everyone who was involved in brainstorming this in the beginning, everyone who put the hard work in to get this done and everyone who filled this out: Y'all are the best.</p>
<p><strong><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1sMxiOd4A_zb48NpW_gd17HQUV2Z2houRRbM4ioDGvTQ/edit?usp=sharing">HERE</a></strong> is the promised link to the complete results. They're in a google slide which is pretty laggy and slow. I'd recommend bookmarking the link and taking a look at it once there aren't so many people trying to access it at the same time.</p>
<p>One more thing before this wraps up, I, Roget, just wanted to give a shoutout to the person who went through the entire survey just to say &quot;all of the groups of interest are tryhard fanfiction nonsense and should be done away with&quot;. I haven't yet been able to understand why you chose to spend an hour of your time to tell me this. While I don't agree with your opinion, I can't help but respect your dedication.</p>

