				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227068" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1581620); return false;" >DarkStuff</a></span> <span class="odate time_1565938930 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">16 Aug 2019 07:02</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4332012">
									

<p>I'm glad to be almost the sole reason that Wondertainment is the second highest in the &quot;activity&quot; category (though I do question, why is GOC so high? I don't see them making many appearances nowadays, maybe I'm just thick headed)</p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Additional&nbsp;Statistics!!</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">Yeah,&nbsp;I&nbsp;wanted&nbsp;more&nbsp;so&nbsp;I&nbsp;made&nbsp;more,&nbsp;and&nbsp;now&nbsp;you&nbsp;can&nbsp;reap&nbsp;the&nbsp;benefits.</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<p><strong>Most Active:</strong> Global Occult Coalition (8.4)<br />
<strong>Least Active:</strong> Alexylva University &amp; SAPPHIRE (2.8)</p>
<p><strong>Most Usable:</strong> Doctor Wondertainment (8.2) <span style="font-size:80%;">fuck yes</span><br />
<strong>Least Usable:</strong> ORIA &amp; Alexylva University (4.3)</p>
<p><strong>Highest Peak:</strong> Church of the Broken God (8.9)<br />
<strong>Lowest Peak:</strong> Alexylva University (5.3)</p>
<p><strong>Worst Worst:</strong> Wilson's Wildlife Solutions (4.9) <span style="font-size:80%;">oh no</span><br />
<strong>Best Worst:</strong> Horizon Initiative (2.7)</p>
<p><strong>Most Original:</strong> Sarkic Cults &amp; Serpent's Hand (8.1)<br />
<strong>Least Original:</strong> GRU Division &quot;P&quot; &amp; Deer College (5.3)</p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">I have one more thing I wanna do but it requires some math, so, I'll do it later&#8230; but I'll start leaking some of it in right now, heheh.</span> Here we are! All the groups ranked, using the average of their scores (don't worry, I inversed &quot;pitfalls&quot; to be accurate). Where there are ties, it's just alphabetical order.</p>
<p><strong>Church of the Broken God:</strong> 7.6<br />
<strong>Doctor Wondertainment:</strong> 7.6<br />
<strong>Global Occult Coalition:</strong> 7.6<br />
<strong>Serpent's Hand:</strong> 7.6<br />
<strong>Marshall, Carter, and Dark:</strong> 7.4<br />
<strong>Are We Cool Yet?:</strong> 7.2<br />
<strong>Sarkic Cults:</strong> 7.2<br />
<strong>Wilson's Wildlife Solutions:</strong> 6.9<br />
<strong>Chaos Insurgency:</strong> 6.8<br />
<strong>Shark Punching Centre:</strong> 6.8<br />
<strong>Unusual Incidents Unit:</strong> 6.7<br />
<strong>Gamers Against Weed:</strong> 6.6<br />
<strong>Anderson Robotics:</strong> 6.4<br />
<strong>The Factory:</strong> 6.4<br />
<strong>Herman Fuller's Circus of the Disquieting:</strong> 6.4<br />
<strong>Prometheus Labs:</strong> 6.3<br />
<strong>Manna Charitable Foundation:</strong> 6.2<br />
<strong>Chicago Spirit:</strong> 6.1<br />
<strong>Fifth Church:</strong> 6.1<br />
<strong>Church of the Second Hytoth:</strong> 5.9<br />
<strong>Oneiroi Collective:</strong> 5.8<br />
<strong>Black Queen:</strong> 5.7<br />
<strong>Ambrose Restaurants:</strong> 5.6<br />
<strong>GRU Division &quot;P&quot;:</strong> 5.6<br />
<strong>SAPPHIRE:</strong> 5.6<br />
<strong>Nobody:</strong> 5.5<br />
<strong>Deer College:</strong> 5.3<br />
<strong>IJAMEA:</strong> 5.3<br />
<strong>Horizon Initiative:</strong> 5.2<br />
<strong>Alexylva University:</strong> 5.0<br />
<strong>ORIA:</strong> 5.0</p>
<p>If this has taught me one thing, it's that Alexylva needs more love. Also, quite a competition for first! Also, if anyone wants to redo this list, taking the &quot;activity&quot; score out of the equation because that doesn't really correlate to quality, be my guest, but I ain't redoing it.</p>
</div>
